        "author": "cedrozor",
        "email": "cedrozor@gmail.com",
        "date": "2020-10-23T14:28:33Z",
        "message": "fixed an issue into FreeRDP with a special copy&paste logic into MS Office applications which disconnected the session after a special paste when pressing the enter key\nthe protocol scheme when sharing a session or creating a session URL is now determined by the HTTP_X_FORWARDED_PROTO http header if available, instead of the current http request, so that https is correctly detected after a redirection by a reverse proxy or a load-balancer",
        "url": "https://github.com/myrtille-rdp/myrtille/commit/87534d15c0ce288c103537db783e2d7d7b26326b"
    },
    {
